Package it.polimi.ingsw.virtualView

Class GameMessage

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.util.Observable<GameMessage>
it.polimi.ingsw.virtualView.GameMessage
public class GameMessage
extends Observable<GameMessage>
GameMessage is the message sent by the remote view (the FrontEnd) to the controller (the BackEnd), it contains the information for an action performed in a player's turn
